Package: pdfdown
Type: Package
Title: Robust Downloads of Portable Document Format (PDF) Files
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Defenders of Wildlife", "ESC", email = "esa@defenders.org",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Jacob Malcom <jmalcom@defenders.org>
Description: Scraping PDFs from the web can run into little hitches that make
    writing a scraper annoying. This simplifies PDF scraping by creating a 
    dedicated function and support functions to, e.g., test for PDFness.
License: BSD_2_clause + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Imports:
    dplyr,
    httr,
    pdftools
